---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Contact Us"
	description="Get in touch with AI Efficiency Hub for questions, feedback, or partnership inquiries."
	pubDate={new Date('January 01 2026')}
	heroImage="/assets/blog-placeholder-about.webp"
>
	<h2>Get in Touch</h2>
	<p>
		Have a question, feedback, or partnership inquiry? We'd love to hear from you.
	</p>

	<h3>Email</h3>
	<p>
		For general inquiries, content suggestions, or business partnerships:
	</p>
	<p>
		<a href="mailto:hello@ai-coding-flow.com" class="contact-email">hello@ai-coding-flow.com</a>
	</p>

	<h3>Content Corrections</h3>
	<p>
		Found an error or outdated information in one of our articles? Let us know and we'll update it promptly.
	</p>

	<h3>Advertising & Partnerships</h3>
	<p>
		Interested in advertising on AI Efficiency Hub or exploring a content partnership?
		Reach out via email with your proposal and we'll respond within 48 hours.
	</p>

	<h3>Response Time</h3>
	<p>
		We typically respond within <strong>1-2 business days</strong>. For urgent matters, please include "URGENT" in your subject line.
	</p>

	<style>
		.contact-email {
			font-size: 1.2rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			color: var(--accent);
			text-decoration: none;
			border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
			padding-bottom: 2px;
			transition: opacity 0.2s;
		}
		.contact-email:hover {
			opacity: 0.8;
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
